# Dependencies — glob v11 requires **/<dir>/** to exclude contents, not just **/<dir>
**/node_modules
**/node_modules/**
**/npm-debug.log
**/yarn-debug.log
**/yarn-error.log
**/.pnpm-debug.log

# Yarn cache (large, not needed in build context)
.yarn/cache
.yarn/cache/**
.yarn/install-state.gz

# Version control
**/.git
**/.git/**
# **/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes
**/.github

# Environment files
**/.env
**/.env-example
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# Build outputs
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/out

# IDE and editor files
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/.DS_Store

# Testing
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output

# Logs
**/logs
**/*.log

# Misc
**/README.md
**/LICENSE
**/*.md
**/*.txt 

# React Router
**/.react-router

# Expo
**/.expo

apps/mobile/caches/*
